=begin pod

=head1 NAME

B<Rakudoc::Utils> - Provides a binary and routines to extract Rakudoc and convert to classes for further word processing.

=head1 SYNOPSIS

=begin code :lang<raku>
$ rakudoc2wp <file with Rakudoc> ofile=/file/path [options...] 
=end code

=head1 DESCRIPTION

B<Rakudoc::Utils> is designed to simplify extracting Rakudoc from a file
and converting it to a user-friendly tree structure for further processing.

It is intended primarily to be used in PDF document production, but it
should be useful in other roles.

